Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用喇叭吹口練習著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:47.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:49.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:55.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真想快點能像梨旺前輩那樣吹曲啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:57.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很斯巴達的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:04.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去吃早餐 食堂在那邊 你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:04.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:15.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光光的 沙沙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後要請你關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠爛的～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:15.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是昨晚用來給你慶祝的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費了點心思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上邊曬著的干魚 你收起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:33.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 乃繪留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡就先吃了早餐再睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:43.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要加油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:44.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位置 是梨旺前輩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 飯都冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:10.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 給你介紹我們第1121小隊的陣容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是小隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西婭·海德曼少尉 坦克指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們相處愉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:22.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:25.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 乃繪留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒風乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:43.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:50.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒風下士 駕駛員 還兼任維修員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 最後的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:03.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨埜谷暮羽二等兵 炮手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:08.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 我雖然比你小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:11.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好歹也比你先到 你得聽我話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筋疲力盡了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 乃繪留
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:30.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:49.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個熏豬肉是我做的 你多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:50.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是行軍還是吹喇叭 身體都是本錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多點長好身體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:10.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:12.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完早餐後 帶她去基地認認路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很忙 但因為是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才迫不得已帶你來認路的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 請多多指教 暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫得這麼親近 空深二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨埜谷二等兵同志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:57.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼首先 向國旗和隊旗致禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:04.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第1121小隊坦克小隊 目前隊員是五名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:12.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內有少尉一 軍士長一 下士一 二等兵二 合計五名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 墨埜谷同志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是最少兵制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:19.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示著…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是少數精英
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:25.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們小隊所配備的裝備是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克一 重機槍一 輕機關鎗二 步槍四 手槍五
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:46.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這些戰力守衛特魯瓦州\N賽茲一帶的國界線就是我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:47.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:53.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨埜谷二等兵同志 我有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:59.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧 允許你提問 空深二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:00.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:05.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人沒記錯的話 賽茲的對面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 山的對面是不毛大地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(398,325)}{\fs14}No Man's Land
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:14.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我國赫爾維西亞就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:19.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這裡就是國境 是最前線 是重要據點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:25.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此值班不能鬆懈 一晚五人輪流 嚴禁打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:31.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是本鎮唯一與首都連接著的熱線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:32.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是響了就表示發生了大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:42.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時將會讓全員起床 馬上進入第一警備陣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 墨埜谷同志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓有隊長室和作戰指揮室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:11.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上進出…自由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要記得敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:15.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒熱水和打掃都是輪流制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:20.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡順序是按軍階排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:34.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起洗比較歡樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是輪到乃繪留嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她好像很累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:49.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長親自幹這粗重活 怎麼給新兵做榜樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:53.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等下會做的 隊長就要應該隊長的樣 擺好架勢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:16.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 你看～好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:20.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是配置給我們第1121小隊的主戰坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:24.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維克塔〇式自動行走坦克 建御雷神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比訓練所的要大很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是所謂零世代的坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:37.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國內剩餘不到10輛 舊時代的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:41.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過 真的是很厲害的坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在修理中 部件不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:56.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然修理手冊也沒留下來 部件也幾乎找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 乃繪留會想辦法的 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不准你說這是花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:10.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終有一天…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別當我是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆鬆垮垮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確我們的部隊是鬆鬆垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人都說我們是賽茲的累贅部隊 是花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:29.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克兵 卻連輛能開的坦克都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就帶到這裡 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就相處得好好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:41.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我們剛見面那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 你去帶小彼去房間睡之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 為什麼她是通信兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:03.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了要裝填手或駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:07.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法 是司令部分配她來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申請不通過是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:11.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:15.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:20.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺一定會如常一樣 好好疼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看她這樣 可是個敏銳的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定察覺到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:42.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是你睡迷糊了吧 乃繪留真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了 幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宿舍那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很正常嗎 幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留你也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:37.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術員就應該用科學的方法搜查後再來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 幽靈什麼的才不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在不存在不存在 絕對不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟你相同意見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 幽靈才不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:01.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對中的絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我仔細地調查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:14.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回不來就吹喇叭 馬上派增援過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 二等兵同志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 彼…二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷感覺就像是進行曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是任務 不是玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 彼…空深二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打前鋒 我掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:45.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就 突入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:05.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這附近是還沒建堡壘之前那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前是幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊狄亞文字 不知道寫了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讀就別去看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讀就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正多半是大老早之前的胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:08.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈不是時刻保佑著我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:15.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生的村子每年都有迎接和感謝幽靈的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪個鄉下出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:25.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂幽靈 會附身 會吸血\N又會舞弄著屍體 專幹壞事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:45.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠會傳染疾病…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你自己不也怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 暮羽…二等兵同志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了下 這裡會不會是學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:29.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的學校 首都也沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 以前的人比現在多很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:38.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以以前在這一定有很多跟我們差不多大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集起來 一起學習…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一定也有教音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都不是軍隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能讀懂文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升D小調
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音 是不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在陶醉什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽 真美妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:36.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:37.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:46.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這賽茲 這堡壘 還有這部隊的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:54.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是鄉下的一個爛部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:01.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克也開不了 補給也經常給我們忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只有一些形式上的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又鬆鬆垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:31.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:53.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是這美妙的\N我最喜愛的第1121小隊的炮手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:03.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭開幽靈的真面目…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:14.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你長得可真像昨天的小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 看我煮了你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:20.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能對受傷的孩子施虐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:23.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子也一定沒有別的去處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們的隊徽是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了它會遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 守子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給它起名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我覺得這很美好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:48.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天差點被它害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天也因此可以大冒險了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:21:00.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 那才不算是冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:04.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這要由投票決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 隊長命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:11.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果你下次再敢偷吃 就要懲罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早是梨旺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:02.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都讓彼方做的話 鎮上的人要發牢騷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:04.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:12.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就是小彼的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:19.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:23.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我碰巧在那邊找到了湊對的椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:26.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是為了你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
